component of $\\delta\\theta_{\\mathrm{STT}}$ in a binary system with two Sun-like\nstars and separation by $\\sim 0.1$ AU if an experiment would be able to measure\n$\\gamma-1$ down to $\\sim 10^{-6}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2012 03:14:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-05"}
