2\"$ resolution, yield $N_\\HI \\approx 1.2 \\times 10^{21} \\cmt$ within the\n\\CII\\ velocity range. Thus, some H$_2$ not detected in CO must be present, in\nagreement with earlier findings based on the SPIRE 250 -- 500 $\\mu$m emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2012 13:46:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
