icity of [Fe/H]=-0.01$\\pm$0.14 dex, while\nNGC 1798 has a slightly lower metal content of [Fe/H]=-0.12$\\pm$0.07 dex.\nFinally, we derive a metallicity of [Fe/H]=-0.38$\\pm$0.06 dex for NGC 2266.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2012 13:54:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
